      "content": "thanks. i checked the transaction logs and they look okay, like the timeouts are happening so fast they don't even leave much of a trail. it feels super random too, like it's not even tied to specific high-traffic times. is there something else that could cause these sudden spikes in connection usage that aren't obvious in the logs?",
